data.description: Welcome Home to this beautiful 4 bedroom 2 1/2 bath ranch. This home features hardwood floors and crown moulding throughout, spacious open floor plan, Gourmet Kitchen with Pass-Through, Formal Dining, and Breakfast Nook. This turn-key home has endless possibilities! Three bedrooms on main level, one having hardwood floors and double doors (features that would make an excellent home office or personal gym). The master bedroom offers a sitting area, access to the screened-in porch and two, YES! TWO CLOSETS! Outdoor living space completes this well-kept home. Don't miss the opportunity to preview today!
